Offering 2900 sq ft on 3 levels with 4 bedrooms, 5 bathrroms (inc. 3 Ensuites) Over height ceilings and extra large windows allow the stunning views to stream into this one of a kind home. The main living area also provides a large 676 sq ft wrap around deck which enhances the overall ambience of the home and property. The layout of this home offers a 1 bedroom suite on the lower level and the 2 bedrooms on the upper floor both offering ensuites making this ideal for long term guest visits or extended families. There is plenty of extra parking for the ATV's, Dirt Bikes and other toys. Great value here with lots of potential.
